        "text_MrhVbz": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Your privacy is respected, and Cedar Hospitality is committed to safeguarding your personal information. This privacy notice will explain how we will handle your personal data when you visit our website (independent of where you are accessing it from), as well as your privacy rights and the legal safeguards in place to ensure your ultimate privacy.<br/><br/>The layered nature of this privacy policy enables you to click through to the specific details that are broken down by important topics of discussion.<br/><br/>We have adopted the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs) contained in the Privacy Act 1988 (Cth) (the Privacy Act). The NPPs govern the way in which we collect, use, disclose, store, secure and dispose of your Personal Information.<br/><br/>A copy of the Australian Privacy Principles may be obtained from the website of The Office of the Australian Information Commissioner at www.aoic.gov.au<br/><br/></p>",
            "text_size": "text-base",
            "text_line_limit": "none",
            "button_style": "btn--underline",
