            "icon": "none",
            "heading": "Cedar Hospitality Contact Details",
            "content": "<p>If you have any queries or complaints about our Privacy Policy please contact us at:</p><p>Our contact details for our Melbourne store are:</p><p><strong>Full Business Name: Cedar Hospitality</strong></p><p><strong>Email Address</strong>: <em>Website Enquiries</em>: <a href=\"mailto:cedarsales@cedarhospitality.com\">cedarsales@cedarhospitality.com</a></p><p><em>  Account Customers & Enquires:</em> <a href=\"mailto:cedarsales@cedarhospitality.com\">cedarsales@cedarhospitality.com</a></p><p><strong>Postal Address:</strong> 223-231 Brunswick Rd, Brunswick, Victoria, 3056, Australia.</p>",
